{"tid":1170325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】美國跨黨派議員去信林鄭促撤草案 斥修例毀港自治無可挽回","createTime":"2019-05-25T02:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T22:05:50.000Z","uid":13663,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"097c8866c27865a116462d8ca14cbbb97b2bde81","tid":1170325,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:32:41.000Z","msg":"美國8名參眾兩院的跨黨派議員聯署去信特首林鄭月娥，要求特區政府撤回修訂《逃犯條例》。信中指憂慮修例後將影響目前美國與香港之間的關係，草案一旦通過，將不可挽回地損害香港所珍惜的高度自治和對人權的保護（irreparably damage Hong Kong&rsquo;s cherished autonomy and protections for human rights），並容許中國政府引渡居於香港商人、記者、人權倡議者以及異見人士。<br />\n<br />\n信中又指出，《逃犯條例》修訂通過後，美國及其他跨國企業可能選擇將總部，由香港遷往亞太其他地區一個「不會將外國公民置於引渡到中國大陸的風險之中」的城市。<br />\n<br />\n聯署的8名議員中，有7名早前出席於美國國會召開，針對香港人權狀況的聽證會。香港眾志亦在facebook轉載有關信件，指今次美國國會多名議員致特首的信函相當少見，印證了「逃犯條例」修訂極之嚴峻的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n8名聯署議員名單<br />\n<br />\n&bull; Massachusetts Congressman Jim McGovern（民主黨眾議員）<br />\n&bull; Florida Senator Marco Rubio（共和黨參議員）<br />\n&bull; New Jersey Congressman Chris Smith（共和黨眾議員）<br />\n&bull; Montana Senator Steve Daines（共和黨參議員）<br />\n&bull; New York Congressman Thomas Suozzi（民主黨眾議員）<br />\n&bull; Arkansas Senator Tom Cotton（共和黨參議員）<br />\n&bull; Florida Congressman Brian Mast（共和黨眾議員）<br />\n&bull; Utah Congressman Ben McAdams（民主黨眾議員）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190525/59639372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59639372&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62L4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=14beb9bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59639372&h=82343ebc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190525/59639372</a>"},{"pid":"24641c7aa74aed639c74e3628a09d8100034804e","tid":1170325,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"香港關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/